21/09/2004
NEW YORK, United States -- Greek Foreign Minister Petros Molyviatis and his Turkish counterpart Abdullah Gul agreed Monday (20 September) that bilateral relations had improved and that further measures to reinforce trust between the two countries should be taken. 
Molyviatis and Gul met at the UN General Assembly's session in New York. 
(ANA - 21/09/04; MPA - 20/09/04)
